 7. the owner of the cat is on the left of the person who's hobby is baking##1
 8. the person who growsrose is the gothic-revival house##1
 9. the futuristic house is the person who's hobby is singing##1
10. the person who growsorchid is on the right of the person drinking coffee##1
11. the person who's hobby is baking is on the left of the owner of the horse##1
12. the person who growsorchid is between the ranch-style house and the person who growssunflower##2
13. the person who's birthday is in august is on the right of the owner of the lizard##1
14. the person who's sport is sailing is on the left of the person drinking coffee##1
